<h3>Pemgarda Info</h3>

<div style="text-align:left">
    <p>
        In March 2024, Invivyd announced FDA authorization for Emergency Use of Pemgarda (formely VYD-222) for pre-exposure prophylaxis (PREP) of COVID-19.
        PEMGARDA (pemivibart) is authorized in the U.S. for PrEP of COVID-19 in certain adults and adolescents with moderate-to-severe immune compromise
    </p>

    <p>Early on, we are trying to share information to help people who may benefit from Pemgarda get educated so they can navigate the medical estabishment.</p>
    <ul>
        <li><a href="/pemgarda#engage-with-doctors">Engaging with your Doctors</a> to get a prescription</li>
        <li><a href="/pemgarda#finding-infusion-centers">Finding an infusion center</a> which can administer Pemgarda</li>
        <li><a href="/pemgarda#navigating-payment">Navigating Payment</a> via Medicare or Private Insurace</li>
